# FinOps knowledge base (empty by default)
#
# Drop your tenant's cost-optimization material here and run:
#     python -m app.rag.ingest
#
# Supported formats: .pdf .docx .md .txt
# Suggested filenames so `detect_tipo` classifies them correctly:
#   - pricing-huawei-ecs-2025.pdf        → pricing
#   - well-architected-cost-optimization.pdf → well_architected
#   - finops-playbook-rightsizing.md      → playbook
#   - tagging-policy.md                   → policy
#   - case-study-storage-tiering.pdf      → case_study
#   - best-practices-reserved-instances.md → best_practice
#
# Nothing in this directory is committed except this README/.gitkeep.
